# Run this on a linux host

# Install Tsung

1) Install Erlang

2) sudo yum -y install erlang perl perl-RRD-Simple.noarch perl-Log-Log4perl-RRDs.noarch gnuplot perl-Template-Toolkit

3) wget http://tsung.erlang-projects.org/dist/tsung-1.6.0.tar.gz
	tar xfz tsung-1.6.0.tar.gz
	cd tsung-1.6.0/
	./configure
	make
	sudo -s make install

4) Make sure 8091 is not blocked
